FBIS4-63600 "drsov100_a_94032" FBIS-SOV-94-100 Daily Report 24 May 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Rybkin Meets Slovak National Council Delegation Rybkin Meets Slovak National Council Delegation LD2405103194 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1021 GMT 24 May 94 LD2405103194 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Moscow May 24 ITAR-TASS -- State Duma Speaker Ivan Rybkin on Tuesday received a Slovak National Council delegation led by Ivan Laluga, chairman of the Foreign Policy Committee, the Duma press service announced. The two sides discussed prospects for an improvement and development of mutually beneficial contacts between Russia and Slovakia in the economic, scientific and cultural fields, pointing out the importance of developing interparliamentary contacts. Laluga conveyed an official invitation from the chairman of the National Council of the Slovak Republic to the State Duma speaker to visit Slovakia at the head of a Russian parliamentary delegation.
